};
</code></pre> <ul> <li>Minimal utility struct used by:</li> <li><code>HashMap::GetPairs</code>.</li> <li><code>LinkedList::printPairList</code>.</li> <li>Does not have comparison operators or methods; equality and hashing are provided elsewhere when needed.</li> </ul>
